signatureAbility.signatureDescription: RAC receivers fight for every possible yard after making a catch. When they enter the zone, this ability increases their success rate on RAC catches against single coverage.
When lined up in the slot, receivers with this ability make faster cuts and have better hands on short routes.
Receivers with this ability run sharper routes and catch more consistently while running cross routes.
Some players thrive on making defenders look silly. When they enter the zone, this ability increases their fakeout rate on the next juke, spin or hurdle.
Ballcarriers with this ability have faster spin animations.
Ballcarriers with this ability have more powerful stiff arm animations.
Aggressive receivers overpower defenders and attack the football. When they enter the zone, this ability increases their success rate on aggressive catches against single coverage.
Receivers with this ability have an increased success rate when running double moves against man coverage.
Receivers with this ability run sharper routes and catch more consistently while running in and out routes.
Defenders with this ability are rarely faked out by ballcarrier moves (and cannot be faked out when user-controlled).
Ballcarriers with this ability have faster and higher hurdle animations.
Ballcarriers with this ability have faster spin animations.
Run Stuffers can singlehandedly disrupt an offense. When they enter the zone, this ability increases their win rate and block shed speed against one-on-one run blocks.
